Bios:
A place to speak up and do something in support of the Black Lives Matter movement. Inspired by Brandi Riley's moving plea in the video posted here.

STATEMENT OF VALUES: 

We believe in freedom of expression and encourage curiosity and respectful debate; 
We respect the diversity of experiences and viewpoints of individuals in this forum; 
We believe that members should be kind in their language and choices here; 
We advocate members taking action towards group goals and hope that information and discussions provide a learning platform upon which to reflect and take thoughtful action;
